Hellenic Techno rights issue approved . The Athens bourse approved the 7 . 7 billion drachma rights issue by Greek construction firm Hellenic Technodomiki . Hellenic Technodomiki will issue 5 , 500 , 000 common registered shares at 1 , 400 drachmas . The terms will be one new share per one outstanding . Proceeds will be used for working capital purposes and new investments in equipment . - - Angelos Kiosklis , Athens Newsroom + 301 3311812 - 4 
